[03:23] <audreyt> {a=>'b'} dispatch to Array

[03:23] <audreyt> er

[03:23] <audreyt> {a=>'b'} dispatch to Hash

[03:23] <audreyt> [1,2,3] to Array

[03:23] <audreyt> (sorry, just woke up.)

