[03:25] <audreyt> like that?

[03:25] <audreyt> PerlJam: er no, that's named and a hash :)

[03:25] * markstos_ checks

[03:26] <audreyt> Pair is when you do   foo('a'=>'b')

[03:26] <audreyt> note the lhs of => is not bare (which would be named)

